Package pacman.util

Enum MusicPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MusicPlayer>
      • pacman.util.MusicPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MusicPlayer>
    public enum MusicPlayer
extends java.lang.Enum<MusicPlayer>

    SceneSwitch

    A MusicPlayer is an object of utility to provide some methods to play sounds in the game.

    Note: this class is implemented an Enum, thus to be a singleton class.

    Usage: 

        SceneSwitch.INSTANCE.{PLAY_ANYTHING}();
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Song Zhang
